Pre-process - factor and scale data

normalize <- function(x) {
  return ((x - min(x)) / (max(x) - min(x)))
}
training_data_pp <- as.data.frame(lapply(training_data, normalize))
test_data_pp <- as.data.frame(lapply(test_data, normalize))
